  "title": "Marketing Assistant",
  "description": "<p>·       In charge of preparing reports based on each customer unique requirements.</p><p>·       Assist marketing team and working cohesively with other team members on existing projects as well as implementation of new projects.</p><p>·       Participate and assist in the coordination and preparation of customers tender/bidding process.</p><p>·       Provide support to the team in providing documents required by internal staff / external customers.</p><p>·       Supervise collection activities.</p><p>·       Liaise with forwarders on containers booking.</p><p>·       Supervise containers loading activities.</p><p>·       Coordinate with Operations team on customers collection.</p><p>·       Administrative support as required.</p><p>·       Other as-hoc duties assigned by reporting officer.</p>",
